#  Aladdin Protocol: Core Blackboard Infrastructure

Welcome to the official repository of **Project SENNEX**. The Aladdin Protocol is an enterprise-grade, decentralized multi-agent architecture operating via a high-throughput, centralized shared memory space (the Blackboard).

##  Key Architectural Pillars
- **Layer 1 Core Orchestration:** Dynamic state routing and semantic bounding using Martingale calculus.
- **Layer 2 Security Mesh:** Triple-layer consensus defense arrays (S6 Latent Guard, S8 Claude reasoning audit, S9 Codex syntax validator, and S10 Mistral cryptographic hashes).
- **Layer 3 Context Memory Bridge:** Highly optimized, asynchronous memory flushing between S3 short-term cache and S4 long-term historical pattern indices.

##  Current Status
Phase 1 (Core Initialization) is officially locked. We are currently scaling our infrastructure nodes and setting up global compliance parameters out of our upcoming Singapore registry.

